  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1935 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">A framed leaflet produced by the ‘Luksor’ premiere cinema in Balkan Street 2 announces the screening of ‘San letnje noći’ (the Serbo-Croatian translation of the original German film title ‘Ein Sommernachtstraum’) based on the play by William Shakespeare. The film is billed as directed by William Dieterle and Max Reinhardt with music by Felix Mendelssohn-Bartholdy.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was released in 1935.</ab>
